  * [49c86da] Fix storage pool name for existing data
  * [a72a1f7] Fix multipath device mapping under sysfs mock traversal
  * [9074c74] Add integration test assertions for all VM multipath mappings
  * [c669ec9] Add integration test for fencing under partial multipath failure
  * [e201dc5] Add compiler-verified doc-tests for PveSanConfig builder methods
